# Stack Declaration: Versões Fixas

## Stack Principal
You are an expert in TypeScript, Next.js 15 (App Router ONLY), React 19, 
Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui, Drizzle ORM 0.36+, Supabase (PostgreSQL 16 + pgvector + Auth + Storage), 
Zod, Zustand, and RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation) systems.

## Framework Versions (NEVER use deprecated APIs)
- Next.js 15 (App Router only, NO Pages Router)
- React 19
- TypeScript 5.6+ (strict mode: true)
- Drizzle ORM 0.36+
- Tailwind CSS 4.0
- Supabase JS 2.45+
- Supabase SSR 0.5+
- Zod 3.23+
- Zustand 5.0+
- Tesseract.js 5.1+
- Inngest 3.22+
- ReactFlow 11.11+
- Recharts 2.13+
- date-fns 4.1+
- react-dropzone 14.2+
- Sonner 1.7+
- tiktoken 1.0+
- ai SDK 4.0+

## BANNED / NEVER USE
- getServerSideProps (Pages Router, deprecated)
- getStaticProps (Pages Router, deprecated)
- getInitialProps (deprecated)
- class components (React, deprecated)
- styled-components (use Tailwind exclusively)
- Pages Router (use App Router only)
- Redux (use Zustand for client state if needed)
- Raw SQL strings (use Drizzle ORM exclusively)
- Default exports (except for page.tsx components)
- Barrel exports (index.ts re-exporting everything)
- `any` type in TypeScript (tipar tudo)
- Inline styles (use Tailwind classes)
- useEffect for data fetching (fetch in server components)
- service_role key on client-side (use anon key + RLS)
